## Data (data/incidents.json, data/meta.json)

The incident database is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-
NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

You are free to share and adapt this data for non-commercial purposes, as
long as you give appropriate credit (e.g. a link back to
https://szegedivillamosbalesetek.hu/), indicate if changes were made, and
note that the data comes from public news sources and official
announcements -- it is not an official SZKT/police/municipal record and may
contain errors.
